{"tid":245274,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[LH情報] 進擊的巨人二期OP《心臓を捧げよ！》完整版釋出+香港公演","createTime":"2017-05-16T06:21:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T04:12:01.000Z","uid":1976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c877934a7c9ffb77d4093439197cf2f619769072","tid":245274,"uid":1976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:21:57.000Z","msg":"唔知有無人知道LH呢樣嘢呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">《心臓を捧げよ！》完整版</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cZ1bAU0DR6o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcZ1bAU0DR6o&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=04c3b5f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cZ1bAU0DR6o</a><br />\n一樣可以聽到唔同SH/LH歌曲嘅節奏<br />\n例如紅蓮の弓矢、自由の翼、Revive以及開頭最明顯嘅聖戦と死神<br />\n可以參考nico片 sm30954673<br />\n開頭例牌加咗句德文（笑）<br />\n最後好似cut咗咁<br />\n其實係因為同下首歌曲做連接<br />\n將整個アルバム變為一個完整故事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Linked Horizon 2nd Album《進撃の軌跡》17/5 發售</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>曲目：<br />\n1.   二ヶ月後の君へ<br />\n2.   紅蓮の弓矢（TVアニメ「進撃の巨人」Season1 前期オープニング主題歌）<br />\n3.   14文字の伝言<br />\n4.   紅蓮の座標（劇場版「進撃の巨人」前編～紅蓮の弓矢～主題歌）<br />\n5.   最期の戦果<br />\n6.   神の御業<br />\n7.   自由の翼（TVアニメ「進撃の巨人」Season1 後期オープニング主題歌）<br />\n8.   双翼のヒカリ<br />\n9.   自由の代償（劇場版「進撃の巨人」後編～自由の翼～主題歌）<br />\n10. 彼女は冷たい棺の中で<br />\n11. 心臓を捧げよ！（TVアニメ「進撃の巨人」Season2オープニング主題歌）<br />\nボーナストラック<br />\n12. 青春は花火のように（TVアニメ「進撃！巨人中学校」オープニング主題歌）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n從曲名都可以見到係充滿SH style<br />\n好期待成個アルバム完整聽一次<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Linked Horizon Live Tour 2017《進撃の軌跡》海外公演 香港出演決定！</strong></span><br />\n21/10 同 22/10 喺九展公演<br />\n如果我可以我想兩埸去齊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港公演由 ED PRODUCTION LIMITED 負責<br />\n可以上去佢FB睇一睇<br />\n<br />\nLH情報到呢度為止<br />\n雖然全部都遲咗少少<br />\n不過希望大家放下正皮畀用電話打呢篇文章嘅我<br />\n同埋希望我傳教成功<br />\n畀更多人認識SH同LH<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13216ac17d666d5d4a3b231e52de9d3e0d7f73d","tid":245274,"uid":1976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2bfc439d208f237702a6415a8bcf6107e781982","tid":245274,"uid":20963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:24:05.000Z","msg":"一定會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78664c9849a40ae6b874a5b79c0e0a8cd863b136","tid":245274,"uid":1976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:24:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好感動<br />\n終於嚟香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72498ef50b72cf4e93fbce8dc1b86d989d452a8","tid":245274,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:26:06.000Z","msg":"中意ed多啲"},{"pid":"01fe2008a345314e39499cc05496794269ad56fd","tid":245274,"uid":1976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:27:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中意ed多啲</blockquote><br />\nSH/LH 曲風初頭其實又真係比較難接受<br />\n佢唔似 J-Pop<br />\n而係故事型式"},{"pid":"a9811bfed663750799891210b03fc1aa65956174","tid":245274,"uid":1976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:28:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中意ed多啲</blockquote><br />\nSH/LH 曲風初頭其實又真係比較難接受<br />\n佢唔似 J-Pop<br />\n而係故事型式</blockquote><br />\n不過一愛上咗就脫唔到坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd78bbc038cecb534fee0c78cde2a376dd6d1e6f","tid":245274,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:28:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中意ed多啲</blockquote><br />\nSH/LH 曲風初頭其實又真係比較難接受<br />\n佢唔似 J-Pop<br />\n而係故事型式</blockquote><br />\n兩首都中意 不過ed洗腦洗到停唔到<img src=\"/a